An ancient war is revived when a young farmer unwittingly opens a gateway between our world and a fearsome race of giants.

Free on Earth for the first time in centuries, the giants seek to reclaim the land they lost in the day, forcing the young Jack (Nicholas Hoult) to fight the battle of his life to stop them. Fighting for a kingdom, its people, and the love of a brave princess, he comes face to face with the unstoppable warriors he thought only existed in legend ... and have the opportunity to become a legend himself.
